", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "Section 901 of the\n\t\t\t Internal Revenue Code of 1986", "@value": "Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:901"}, {"#tail": "as", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "subsection (n)", "@value": "Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:901/ss:n"}, {"#tail": "and by inserting after", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "subsection (o)", "@value": "Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:901/ss:o", "@proposed": "true"}, {"#tail": "the following new\n\t\t\t subsection:", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "subsection (m)", "@value": "Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:901/ss:m"}], "#text": "\n            ", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "(a)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "In\n\t\t\t general"}, "quoted-block": {"@style": "OLC", "after-quoted-block": {"#tail": "\n          ", "#text": "."}, "#tail": "\n        ", "subsection": {"#tail": "\n            ", "enum": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "(n)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n              ", "#text": "Special rules\n\t\t\t\trelating to major integrated oil companies which are dual capacity\n\t\t\t\ttaxpayers"}, "paragraph": [{"continuation-text": {"#tail": "\n              ", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": ".", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "subparagraph (B)", "@value": "Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:901/ss:n/p:1/sp:B", "@proposed": "true"}, "@continuation-text-level": "paragraph", "#text": "Nothing in this paragraph shall be\n\t\t\t\tconstrued to imply the proper treatment of any such amount not in excess of the\n\t\t\t\tamount determined under", "@commented": "no"}, "#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n                ", "{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}entity-ref": {"#tail": ") to a foreign country or possession of the United States for any\n\t\t\t\tperiod shall not be considered a tax\u2014", "@entity-type": "act", "#text": "section\n\t\t\t\t167(h)(5)", "@value": "Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:167/ss:h/p:5"}, "#text": "Notwithstanding any\n\t\t\t\tother provision of this chapter, any amount paid or accrued by a dual capacity\n\t\t\t\ttaxpayer which is a major integrated oil company (within the meaning of", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(1)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "General\n\t\t\t\trule"}, "@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#text": "\n                ", "@id": "idA86BDC3205EF48378545D9D088E03443", "@commented": "no", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "if, for such period, the foreign country or\n\t\t\t\tpossession does not impose a generally applicable income tax, or", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(A)"}, "@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "idCE1206A91A254CEFA030EAF1D94F610A", "@commented": "no"}, {"@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "to the extent such amount exceeds the\n\t\t\t\tamount (determined in accordance with regulations) which\u2014", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(B)"}, "clause": [{"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "is paid by such dual capacity taxpayer\n\t\t\t\tpursuant to the generally applicable income tax imposed by the country or\n\t\t\t\tpossession, or", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(i)"}, "@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#text": "\n                    ", "@id": "id3616EAF2E4174061B78DB6C614CBB2C4", "@commented": "no"}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "would be paid if the generally applicable\n\t\t\t\tincome tax imposed by the country or possession were applicable to such dual\n\t\t\t\tcapacity taxpayer.", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(ii)"}, "@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#text": "\n                    ", "@id": "idBBD48C80AE584E7AAE22BC2F3F750626", "@commented": "no"}], "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "id1430720C4FEC4AF1BAEDD845D4A2DE7E", "@commented": "no"}]}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n                ", "term": {"#tail": "means, with respect to\n\t\t\t\tany foreign country or possession of the United States, a person who\u2014", "#text": "dual capacity taxpayer"}, "#text": "For purposes of this\n\t\t\t\tsubsection, the term", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(2)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "Dual capacity\n\t\t\t\ttaxpayer"}, "@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#text": "\n                ", "@id": "id2BE54CFB0E9F46AEABB5E04C1E1553D1", "@commented": "no", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "is subject to a levy of such country or\n\t\t\t\tpossession, and", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(A)"}, "@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "id114FA007ACB04E589C34FD9AE707FF40", "@commented": "no"}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "receives (or will receive) directly or\n\t\t\t\tindirectly a specific economic benefit (as determined in accordance with\n\t\t\t\tregulations) from such country or possession.", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(B)"}, "@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "idB48A3E58EACB4262A062681509EBC2D3", "@commented": "no"}]}, {"#tail": "\n            ", "text": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "For\n\t\t\t\tpurposes of this subsection\u2014", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "(3)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                ", "#text": "Generally\n\t\t\t\tapplicable income tax"}, "@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#text": "\n                ", "@id": "id4221398EC1FE4603A1915AC3F6F4FF31", "@commented": "no", "subparagraph": [{"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n                ", "term": {"#tail": "means an income tax (or a series\n\t\t\t\tof income taxes) which is generally imposed under the laws of a foreign country\n\t\t\t\tor possession on income derived from the conduct of a trade or business within\n\t\t\t\tsuch country or possession.", "#text": "generally applicable income tax"}, "#text": "The term", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(A)"}, "header": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "In\n\t\t\t\tgeneral"}, "@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#text": "\n                  ", "@id": "id9A25BF879E264980B24CFC517824B854", "@commented": "no"}, {"#tail": "\n              ", "text": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "Such term shall not include a tax unless it\n\t\t\t\thas substantial application, by its terms and in practice, to\u2014", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "(B)"}, "clause": [{"#tail": "\n                  ", "text": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "persons who are not dual capacity\n\t\t\t\ttaxpayers, and", "@display-inline": "yes-display-inline"}, "enum": {"#tail": "\n                    ", "#text": "(i)"}, "@display-inline": "no-display-inline", "#text": "\n                    ", "@id": "id8EFBAC16675449C2ABDBF167616DBFA1", "@commented": "no"}, {"#tail": "\n                ", "text": {"#tail": "\n                  ", "#text": "persons who are citizens or residents of\n\t\t\t\tthe foreign country or\n\t\